Example of Jenkins PHP CI for Connexion Point Development

The structure of your project should be as follows:

Project
==================================================================
build.properties    (Build properties for Jenkins)
build.xml           (Build script for Jenkins)
php.properties      (Jenkins PHP Environment Settings)
src                 (Directory containing your project)
test                (Directory containing your unit tests, etc..)
resources           (Resource folder for Jenkins)
README              (This file)



Connection Point PEAR Channel
==================================================================
jenkins-dev.connexionpoint.com


Recommended IDE's
==================================================================
Netbeans: https://netbeans.org/downloads/



